OL,6,F"Over the last two to three years
OL,7,Fthough, we've seen a significant
OL,8,Fuplift in wholesale market prices,
OL,9,Fpower prices, in Europe.
OL,11,F"We've been tremendously successful at
OL,12,Fsheltering islanders from the brunt of
OL,13,Fthat, but unfortunately, yes, prices
OL,14,Fare coming down but they're settling
OL,15,Fat a level that is raised compared to
OL,16,Fwhat they were pre-Russian invasion of
OL,17,FUkraine and obviously we're incurring
OL,18,Fmore costs and unfortunately we're
OL,19,Fgoing to have to increase prices to
OL,20,Fconsumers to cover those costs."
