OL,6,FThe JE boss also says Jersey's
OL,7,Felectricity prices will remain
OL,8,Fconsiderably cheaper than in Guernsey,
OL,9,Fthe UK and the Isle of Man.
OL,11,FHe says he expects to see Jersey's
OL,12,Felectricity charges to stay 30%
OL,13,Fcheaper than in Guernsey and 50% lower
OL,14,Fthan in the UK after the tariff
OL,15,Fincrease.
