OL,6,FWhen asked why the tariff was being
OL,7,Fincreased above the current rate of
OL,8,Finflation in Jersey (5%), Mr Ambler
OL,9,Fsaid: "We need to cover our costs and
OL,10,Fwe need to make sure that we can pay
OL,11,Four bills and if we don't pay our
OL,12,Fbills then, of course, the French will
OL,13,Fcut us off so we've got to service our
OL,14,Fobligations as well.
OL,16,F"What I would say is that over a five-
OL,17,Fyear and 10-year period we've been
OL,18,Ftracking in and around inflation so
OL,19,Fthe performance, the price performance
OL,20,Fof the group is extremely good."
